00:18:47,844 --> 00:18:51,079
mogli da imate. Oprostite,
danas sam malo rastrojen.

208
00:18:51,275 --> 00:18:53,963
Prošlo je dugo otkad smo
bilo kuda išli.

209
00:18:59,876 --> 00:19:02,343
Budite dobri prema njemu i on
ce biti dobar prema Vama.

210
00:19:02,492 --> 00:19:04,640
