269
00:30:20,073 --> 00:30:21,617
Greta?

270
00:30:22,925 --> 00:30:24,647
Hej, jesi li tu?

271
00:30:27,052 --> 00:30:28,984
Izvini.
-Šta se desilo?

272
00:30:29,075 --> 00:30:31,360
Ništa, to je Brams.
-Brams?

273
00:30:32,223 --> 00:30:33,745
On je lutka.

274
00:32:50,869 --> 00:32:52,499
Moja odeca.

275
00:33:10,909 --> 00:33:12,381
Zdravo!

276
00:33:15,284 --> 00:33:17,646
Malkolme, ako si to ti,
nije smešno.

277
00:33:21,078 --> 00:33:23,025
Ako je neko gore...

278
00:33:48,225 --> 00:33:49,725
Zdravo?

279
00:33:59,125 --> 00:34:00,825
Ima li koga?

280
00:34:37,909 --> 00:34:39,450
Malkolme!

281
00:34:39,750 --> 00:34:41,197
Gore!

282
00:34:41,943 --> 00:34:43,439
Malkolme!

283
00:34:46,835 --> 00:34:48,398
Ne! Malkolme!

284
00:35:13,205 --> 00:35:14,613
Ne!

285
00:35:16,767 --> 00:35:18,483
Bože! Gore!

286
00:35:21,659 --> 00:35:23,261
Malkolme!

287
00:35:29,893 --> 00:35:31,420
Greta!

288
00:35:44,978 --> 00:35:48,034
Ne. Malkolme! Malkolme!

289
