359
00:42:39,199 --> 00:42:41,777
To što se dogodilo je
njegova krivica.

360
00:42:41,977 --> 00:42:44,077
Sve ono što ti je oduzeo...

361
00:42:44,278 --> 00:42:46,807
Necu da citam šta god da mi
je taj kuckin sin bude poslao.

362
00:42:47,636 --> 00:42:49,634
Sve se dešava sa razlogom.

363
00:43:09,390 --> 00:43:10,937
Zdravo.

364
00:43:44,236 --> 00:43:46,120
Bože.

365
00:44:50,880 --> 00:44:52,432
Halo?

366
00:44:56,370 --> 00:44:57,856
Halo?

367
00:44:58,556 --> 00:45:00,156
Greta?

368
00:45:09,722 --> 00:45:11,199
Halo?

369
