374
00:45:24,440 --> 00:45:26,937
Zašto ne poštuješ pravila?

375
00:45:28,423 --> 00:45:30,010
Ostavi me na miru!

376
00:45:36,462 --> 00:45:38,393
Šta to radiš?!

377
00:46:06,218 --> 00:46:08,521
Obecavam da cu biti dobar.

378
00:46:10,462 --> 00:46:12,494
Ovaj je tvoj omiljeni.

379
00:48:01,435 --> 00:48:03,774
Da li ovo zaista želiš?

380
00:48:09,601 --> 00:48:11,336
U redu.

381
00:48:17,120 --> 00:48:19,631
Halo?
-Greta, Malkolm je.

382
00:48:20,250 --> 00:48:21,834
Zdravo.

383
