389
00:48:37,823 --> 00:48:39,998
Ne radi se o mojim cipelama.

390
00:48:40,640 --> 00:48:43,420
Nisam siguran da te razumem.
Pozvao sam te...

391
00:48:43,922 --> 00:48:45,997
Moram da idem.

392
00:48:46,631 --> 00:48:48,209
Greta?

393
00:49:09,992 --> 00:49:12,180
Vreme je, dušo.

394
00:50:30,750 --> 00:50:32,382
Buðenje.

395
00:50:51,145 --> 00:50:53,436
Prišla sam vratima i videla kako se

396
00:50:53,536 --> 00:50:56,819
